node.text: Give them all free bobs and vagene!
Wait..the homeless?those people doesnt seems homeless🤣🤣

👏😍 A group of youths, aged 17 to 18, have come together as commUNITY SG to raise funds for homeless individuals in Singapore.

They are working with New Hope Community Services (NHCS) to provide temporary shelter to serve displaced families and individuals.
👍🏻👍🏻. Thank you for giving back to the community
It’s really heartwarming to see this, keep up the good work, you guys are really amazing! 💙
